  val tags = row.getString(2).trim.split("\\|")
  TaggedItem(id, title, tags)
})

paragraphs.title: Calculate Jaccard Similarity between all Items above a threshold
paragraphs.text:
import com.advancedspark.ml.Similarity

val minJaccardSimilarityThreshold = 0.01

val similarItemPairsAboveThresholdRDD = allItemPairsRDD
  .map(itemPair => (itemPair._1.id, itemPair._2.id, Similarity.getJaccardSimilarity(itemPair._1, itemPair._2)))
  .filter(_._3 >= minJaccardSimilarityThreshold) // Preserve only pairs above min jaccard similarity 
  .cache()

val similarItemPairIdCount = similarItemPairIdsAboveThresholdRDD.count()
